sentences.english: A new introduction has been prefixed to the third printing of the book.
sentences.chinese: 本書第三次印刷時前面增加了一篇新的序言。

sentences.english: I took three consecutive shots from beyond the three-point line and made all three-perfectly.
sentences.chinese: 我連續三次在三分線外遠投，三個都進得很漂亮。

sentences.english: This is my third visit in just over two years as Secretary-General of the United Nations.
sentences.chinese: 這是我擔任聯合國祕書長兩年多來的第三次訪問。

sentences.english: It would have been Hefner's third marriage.
sentences.chinese: 這原本將是赫夫納的第三次婚姻。

sentences.english: She is very religious and goes to church three times a week.
sentences.chinese: 她非常虔誠，每週去教堂三次。

sentences.english: It at least underwent threehydrothermal superpositions.
sentences.chinese: 至少經歷有三次熱液迭加。

sentences.english: Missing three tests results in an automatic two-year ban.
sentences.chinese: 缺席三次藥檢的結果是自動禁賽兩年。

sentences.english: I have been out two or three times. But I'm sure there's more to see.
sentences.chinese: 我出去過兩三次，但是我相信一定還有我沒試過的。

sentences.english: You can also provide custom function made of points of cubic bezier curve.
sentences.chinese: 你還可以提供由三次貝塞爾曲線製成的自定義函數。

sentences.english: There is only one practicing spot here in Liuyang. I have been there for only three times.
sentences.chinese: 在瀏陽只有一個高爾夫場地，我去過三次。

sentences.english: The item 4 includes the explanation that three public announcements have been made within liquidation period;
sentences.chinese: 第4項應包括清算期內已公告三次的說明。

sentences.english: I gave up after two or three visits because I found it hard to find the time.
sentences.chinese: 去了兩三次後我放棄了，因爲我抽不出時間。

sentences.english: This is the third time the tourists squawked about the service of the hotel.
sentences.chinese: 這是旅客們第三次對飯店的服務發牢騷了。

sentences.english: This was his third resting-place in the land.
sentences.chinese: 這已經是他第三次休息位，在土地。

sentences.english: Sean had already made three dives earlier in the day on that sameexact spot.
sentences.chinese: 在那一天，同一個潛水地點，西恩已經潛過三次了。

sentences.english: I watch the sunset forty-three times a day.
sentences.chinese: 我看日落四十一天三次。
